{"tid":2118440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】政府研押後選舉真空期安排　《信報》：現屆議員或可續審法案","createTime":"2020-07-21T12:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T13:31:14.000Z","uid":216443,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee9969a3bfbf5fb2a0c27fb37a22a0cbb54428e","tid":2118440,"uid":216443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/21145340/image1595314285852.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21145340%2Fimage1595314285852.png&h=ac3d2615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎在香港的疫情持續，社會關注9月6日的立法會選舉能否如期舉行。《信報》引述消息指，多名建制和民主派人士都評估政府叫停選舉的機會越來越大，而官場中人認為，政府除了可引用《立法會條例》第44條，因應任何危害公眾健康事故把選舉押後兩周外，亦可祭出緊急法，無限期推遲選舉，但預期會承受民主派炮轟和國際輿論壓力。<br />\n<br />\n至於如何處理沒有立法會的真空期，報道指政府正研究引用《立法會條例》第11條，由特首召開立法會「緊急會議」，上屆會期的議員自動成為立法會「緊急會議」議員，審理法案。不過有建制派人士關注緊急會議的權力，是否等同一般大會，有權審理《財政預算案》。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟日報》政情專欄亦引述消息稱，押後選舉期間，剛落任的立法會議員可在議會真空期繼續「頂住先」。資深政圈中人更向該報明言，一旦決定壓後選舉，起碼是半年或一年。報道亦指出，「事實上，北京亦不希望見到去年區議會選舉建制大敗的情況重現」。<br />\n<br />\n政制及事務局回覆傳媒查詢時表示，疫情預計在短期內不會消退，將和食物食物及衞生局，及衞生防護中心緊密聯繫、密切注視疫情的發展，從現在至選舉舉行期間，不斷評估疫情對立法會換屆選舉所造成的影響，並及早因應疫情發展制訂各種預案。"},{"pid":"98e8d295af19eb179d8c71966dd4629a4fa731a4","tid":2118440,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"支持永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca220fe907c0e7546d0541b5c017f09179052be","tid":2118440,"uid":21493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98e8d295af19eb179d8c71966dd4629a4fa731a4","tid":2118440,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"支持永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"萬年國會go"},{"pid":"4e8fef60ef155c8eeee80a3205606c7e71eba9f6","tid":2118440,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"永續立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次就近選期就大爆發"},{"pid":"49109c1e305b115751987d469faad897ececd947","tid":2118440,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"唔敢相信早幾個月講過嘅野會有可能成真<br />\n雖然我只係鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ed9ee3ff965efbd5296659f664302ebed6c446","tid":2118440,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"不如叫埋美國大選 都押後，侵侵繼續執政！"},{"pid":"fe941c515946cdd83b64f6c8b63767d2c77ec88a","tid":2118440,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"加速主義好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17573ae706827b1fb495eda785cfce33febb15d1","tid":2118440,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:31:14.000Z","msg":"班農：我們要給中共72小時最後通牒！<br />\n<br />\n如果在72小時內，中共不開放實驗室，不公開真相，就落下重錘！<br />\n停止無聊的遊戲，停止無意義的爭論<br />\n行動！行動！行動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1285352804735836161?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1285352804735836161%3Fs%3D20&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=c18328a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1285352804735836161%3Fs%3D20&h=7094ad6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1285352804735836161?s=20</a>"}]}